Text.string: Fear not, I'm here to help... you die!
Let's make some wounds. I LOVE wounds!
I can recommend a vet for your friends!
Let's get you to triage, soldier!
Ooh! Now I'm a field medic!
You're gonna feel a little pressure!
Any trauma I can help with or should we make some?
Hope you've got insurance! I won't take it but I hope you've got it!
Got your results back! I'm fatal!
Back to whatever I was doing before.
That's not how I usually lose patients!
Would you like to schedule a follow-up?
You'll miss me when you're injured!
Is that where your heart is?
The shoulder's connected to the... bone bone.
Don't worry, I minored in shoulder!
Do you think I broke anything? Be honest.
This is WAY more fun than healing!
Does it hurt when I do THIS?!
Little something I've been working on.
Laser surgery is all the rage!
I know what I'm doing! Mostly!
Not letting you die on me!
In all my years of practice...
Let's get you to the lab!
I can't treat what I can't see!
Come back and finish your exam!
Sorry I'm not home right now, I'm floating in a Siren's web...
You're a big one, aren't you?
Let me look at your chart!
You brought your own organ donor!
How about you DON'T do that?
You can't get wounded back there.
But I want you nice and wounded.
You'll wanna get that checked out.
Swaths of destruction are my favorite swaths!
More! Give me more to fix!
Put a sheet over the deceased!
A moment of silence... All done!
This never gets any easier! [whistles casually]
Are you hurt? You look hurt.
Won't be able to play piano anymore...
These used to be big, strong hands...
Now, hold still! I just want to give you a shot!
You don't look so good! But I do!
Your blood pressure is over zero. WAY too high!
Let's fix you up, shall we?
You'll be back at it in no time!
You don't care that I'm not licensed, right?
If at first you keep killing your patients, try and try again!
If this works out, leave me a good review!
Relax, I sorta know what I'm doing.
I'm the one they call Doctor Feel-better!
Laughter is the best medicine! [laugh into cough]
It worked? I mean, of course! It worked!
I've removed the cause but not the symptom!
Do not use while operating heavy machinery!
Four out of five doctors agree you're a dick!
Leave your info with the nurse!
Is there a doctor in the house?
Near death experience? Nope! Real thing...
I see a tunnel and a bright light... Kidding, that's not a thing.
This is exactly what I wanted to avoid.
The doctor has left the building!
Don't move! You'll just make it worse!
Follow my finger. Good! You're almost dead!
Time of death: any second now!
Ech. Got a little human on me.
Is there a history of asshole in your family?
You want the good news or the real news?
Your chart says you're gonna die soon!
Be patient! Sorry, little medical humor.
What seems to be the problem?
Show me where it's about to hurt!
Halt and be healed! Or hurt!
I just need to take some blood!
You're in luck! I've got an opening!
The doctor will see you now!
I'm not aiming for your heart but aorta!
Take two of these and die by morning!
Time for a taste of your own medicine!
Scared enough to make a stool sample?
Stand still, I want clean exit wounds!
I don't want to get shot.
It's like med school all over again!
Thanks for doing all that damage!
Aw, and I didn't get YOU anything!
It's okay. I can fix everyone! I hope.
Time to discern the cause of many deaths.
